  <brief_title>Study of Aprepitant / Fosaprepitant for the Prevention of Chemotherapy-induced Nausea and Vomiting (CINV) in Colorectal Cancer Patients - SENRI Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multicenter Randomized Controlled Trial of Combination Antiemetic Therapy With Aprepitant / Fosaprepitant in Patients With Colorectal Cancer Receiving Oxaliplatin-based Chemotherapy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
